  10 Nov 2008; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> irssi-svn-0.3.ebuild:
  Move ChangeLog creation to ESVN_BOOTSTRAP, this makes it work with current
  svn code.

  14 Jul 2008; Javier Villavicencio <the_paya@gentoo.org>
  irssi-svn-0.3.ebuild:
  Keyworded ~x86-fbsd wrt bug #230949.

  07 Jan 2007; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> irssi-svn-0.3.ebuild:
  Drop the extern inline workaround, irssi doesn't use them anymore.

  13 Oct 2006; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> irssi-svn-0.3.ebuild:
  Adust the irssi and silc-client blockers.

  15 Sep 2006; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> irssi-svn-0.3.ebuild:
  Remove trailing slash from ESVN_REPO_URI, thanks to Emanuele Giaquinta.

  01 Aug 2006; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> irssi-svn-0.3.ebuild:
  Port changes from the regular irssi package to irssi-svn.

  18 Mar 2006; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> irssi-svn-0.3.ebuild:
  Remove the old irssi-cvs blocker.

  23 Feb 2006; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> irssi-svn-0.3.ebuild:
  Create the ChangeLog from upstream subversion repository, should fix bug
  #116958.

  28 Nov 2005; <mcumming@gentoo.org> irssi-svn-0.3.ebuild:
  Switched from perl-module to perl-app eclass

  30 Jul 2005; Aaron Walker <ka0ttic@gentoo.org> irssi-svn-0.3.ebuild:
  Added ~mips.

  28 Jun 2005; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> irssi-svn-0.3.ebuild:
  Added NOCONFIGURE=1 to avoid running configure during bootstrap.

  26 Jun 2005; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> irssi-svn-0.3.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc keyword wrt bug #96775.

  25 Jun 2005; Rene Nussbaumer <killerfox@gentoo.org> irssi-svn-0.3.ebuild:
  Added to ~hppa.

